&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The World Health Organization (WHO) coined the term &amp;quot;Disease X&amp;quot; in 2018 as a placeholder for an unpredictable and unknown pathogen that could trigger a devastating global health crisis.&lt;/li&gt;
