	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-1757fdea-7fff-90b9-ca67-59f8dd3b1c3f&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; text-wrap-mode: wrap;&quot;&gt;Disease X is not a specific illness but a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; text-wrap-mode: wrap;&quot;&gt;conceptual placeholder&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; text-wrap-mode: wrap;&quot;&gt; representing the risk of an unknown pathogen capable of causing a pandemic.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; text-wrap-mode: wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-1757fdea-7fff-90b9-ca67-59f8dd3b1c3f&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; text-wrap-mode: wrap;&quot;&gt;COVID-19 is widely regarded as the first real-world example of Disease X.&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-1757fdea-7fff-90b9-ca67-59f8dd3b1c3f&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; text-wrap-mode: wrap;&quot;&gt;Hence, point 2 is correct.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
